<br>
A mage pulls with malise, sics pet, flame shields and nukes away.  The whole fight is less then 30 seconds and then the magician meds for a bit.<br>
<br>
The Necro pulls with darkness, sics pet, fears, dots, refears, redarks, fears, meds, fears, etc.  The whole fight last 2 minutes then they do it again.<br>
<br>
A necro has lots of tools and options but he lacks raw fire power.  A magicain has the fire power (stronger pet and DDs) but he lacks other options.  <br>
<br>
A magician can solo some mobs that a necro can not and a necro can solo mobs that a magician can not.  It comes down to which style you like.  I personally am addicted to the raw power of the magician.  I am sure there are those that love the flexibility of the Necro.<br>
<br>
Try them both.  Talk to magicians and necros.  Play which ever you like.  <br>
<br>
