<br>
I'm not even sure what this horrible garbled sentence is supposed to mean, but I'll assume that you're trying to say that if a Necro gets a MoB on him without a pet he's dead. Well, for one thing, for a mage, that very strongly holds true. For a necro, sorry buddy, complete opposite. If I have a pet and a MoB is going apeshit trying to kill me that pet is a PROBLEM. You cannot FD with a pet up, MoBs will see through it. If you mez, and you have even a little bit of lag when you hit your /pet back off key your pet can then break the mez, although that normally isn't a problem. Root's great, but then after you back off you have to mez-/pet back off again anyway.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Mages are a great class. Yes in most fights they'll outdamage a necromancer. Yes their pets are better. Yes mages get nice nukes. Yes mages have great damage shields. But discounting everything a necromancer can do is idiocy; in a small/weak group there is no better class to have. A necromancer is VASTLY better suited to survival. A necromancer solos about as well as a mage, better in some places, worse in others. In many situations I have had to take over being main healer for a group, and no, I can't heal as well as a dedicated class, but it's pretty damned good for a caster. At times I've had to take over crowd control, and nope, I'm not as well suited to it as a bard or chanter, but I can. <br>
<br>
<br>
There is no class in this game as versatile a necromancer, mages are a specialized damage dealing class with a few useless summons thrown in for flavour. Know these two things and base your judgment off of that. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/umathas.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mathas</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://mathas.tripod.com/leafico.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#333333>(5/8/01 7:47:25 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=41.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://mathas.tripod.com/faceico.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Mage vs. necro</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Mage in group, to many mobs Mage solo 1 and group get the others.<br>
